I was passing close to here,
so I just dropped by.

208
00:11:43,269 --> 00:11:44,603
Is Ryo out working?

209
00:11:44,603 --> 00:11:46,372
Yeah, sort of.

210
00:11:46,372 --> 00:11:47,805
Did something happen?

211
00:11:48,874 --> 00:11:51,741
It's nothing big, but just now, at the park...

212
00:11:56,916 --> 00:12:00,720
