toiletries and clothing?

213
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:03,622
Well, this conflict might be
prolonged, you know?

214
00:12:03,622 --> 00:12:05,291
I brought ten days' worth of clothing.

215
00:12:05,291 --> 00:12:06,849
Ten days' worth?!

216
00:12:07,993 --> 00:12:11,731
Wait, that means there are ten days'
worth of underwear!

217
00:12:11,731 --> 00:12:13,599
