229
00:12:56,442 --> 00:13:00,208
Who are you really, Mr. Saeba?

230
00:13:01,013 --> 00:13:04,416
There's no way a normal detective
would have a gun.

231
00:13:04,416 --> 00:13:06,652
But then, you don't look like a
police detective either.

232
00:13:06,652 --> 00:13:09,712
Maybe I'm a killer for hire.

233
00:13:10,122 --> 00:13:12,818
Yes, you have that dangerous
scent about you.

234
00:13:13,759 --> 00:13:16,284
Do you not like a dangerous scent?

235
00:13:16,729 --> 00:13:19,994
No way! I love it!

236
00:13:20,766 --> 00:13:23,235
And which park is this?

237
00:13:23,235 --> 00:13:27,072
It's the park near Mitsuboshi Bank. Why?

238
00:13:27,072 --> 00:13:29,141
Oh, just wondering.


239
00:13:29,141 --> 00:13:31,473
Well, I think I'll be going home now.

240
00:13:33,012 --> 00:13:35,347
Bye, say hi to Ryo for me.

241
00:13:35,347 --> 00:13:36,871
Okay, bye.

242
00:13:37,483 --> 00:13:39,951
I wonder what she came here for?

243
00:13:48,394 --> 00:13:51,030
Say, is there anything I can do to help?

244
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:53,465
Don't worry about it.

245
00:13:53,465 --> 00:13:57,102
Oh, could you go get Ryo soon?
I think he's in the basement.

246
00:13:57,102 --> 00:13:58,228
Okay!

247
00:14:21,527 --> 00:14:25,657
That serious expression isn't like the
Mr. Saeba I've known so far.

248
00:14:26,599 --> 00:14:28,567
Hitomi, welcome!

249
00:14:29,602 --> 00:14:31,001
It's his usual expression.

250
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:33,037
Here.

251
00:14:33,906 --> 00:14:37,042
It's heavy. It really feels solid.

252
00:14:37,042 --> 00:14:38,143
You want to try firing it?

253
00:14:38,143 --> 00:14:40,634
What?! May I?!

254
00:14:41,447 --> 00:14:42,914
All right!

255
00:14:43,315 --> 00:14:46,852
It's saved my life many times over.

256
00:14:46,852 --> 00:14:48,520
But...

257
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,989
But?

258
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:52,719
I've hurt just as many people with it.

259
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:56,926
That is the way of guns.

260
00:14:59,865 --> 00:15:02,459
