265
00:15:25,591 --> 00:15:26,792
You stay here!

266
00:15:26,792 --> 00:15:28,384
What?! Mr. Saeba!

267
00:15:49,281 --> 00:15:51,146
Now, stay quiet!

268
00:15:57,323 --> 00:15:59,587
I'll save Miss Kaori!

269
00:16:07,299 --> 00:16:08,766
Mr. Saeba, get in!

270
00:16:09,535 --> 00:16:10,402
Can you do this?

271
00:16:10,402 --> 00:16:11,369
You can count on me!

272
00:16:19,345 --> 00:16:21,146
I did it again.

273
00:16:21,146 --> 00:16:22,443
Now, look here...

274
00:16:23,315 --> 00:16:25,651
We were this close to saving her!

275
00:16:25,651 --> 00:16:29,688
If something happens to Miss Kaori,
it'll be my fault!

276
00:16:29,688 --> 00:16:31,757
There's no need to worry about that.

277
00:16:31,757 --> 00:16:33,520
The one they're after isn't Kaori.

278
00:16:34,226 --> 00:16:36,662
If they were after Kaori from the beginning,

279
00:16:36,662 --> 00:16:39,064
