just for hitting them?

286
00:17:05,924 --> 00:17:07,152
Hitting them?

287
00:17:12,965 --> 00:17:14,466
Oh, no! I'm sorry!

288
00:17:14,466 --> 00:17:15,899
Damn! Just go!

289
00:17:19,505 --> 00:17:22,608
