is lure them inside.

299
00:18:05,684 --> 00:18:08,754
It's an old rule of thumb: Kill all witnesses.

300
00:18:08,754 --> 00:18:10,556
Don't hold it against us.

301
00:18:10,556 --> 00:18:13,258
We went to a lot of trouble to
get hold of a gun.

302
00:18:13,258 --> 00:18:17,285
It'll be pointless if we don't see
a profit from it after all.

303
00:18:21,733 --> 00:18:24,964
You didn't have to go wear Kaori's
battle getup, you know.

304
00:18:26,071 --> 00:18:31,043
Wearing this makes me feel like I can
feel Kaori Sempai's courage.

305
00:18:31,043 --> 00:18:34,947
